Package ch.zhaw.it.pm3.spacerunner.domain.spaceelement

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Asteroid
    Asteroid is a type of obstacle in the Space-Runner Game, which moves diagonally.
    Coin
    Coin is a SpaceElement that can be collided with and picked up by the SpaceShip to increase the coin count.
    Obstacle
    Obstacle is an abstract class.
    Rocket
    Rocket is a type of obstacle in the Space-Runner Game, which moves horizontally in a straight line.
    SpaceElement
    SpaceElement is the superclass to all Elements in the game (including SpaceShip, Coin, SpaceWorld and Obstacles) It contains the code for initialization, movement and collision of these Elements.
    SpaceElementTest  
    SpaceShip
    SpaceShip is the SpaceElement that the player controls.
    SpaceShipTest  
    SpaceWorld
    The background of the game.
    SpaceWorldTest  
    UFO
    UFO is a type of obstacle in the Space-Runner Game, which moves to the left in a wavey motion.
    UFOTest  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SpaceShipDirection
    The directions that the SpaceShip can move in.
